document.full_text: seventeen-year-old matteo manassero's malaysian open win has catapulted him from 57th to 33rd in the world rankings, earning him a place at this year's u.s. open, british open and u.s. pga championship.
document.title: manassero's malaysian victory books ticket to the majors
